    "attributes": {
        "action": "New laws/fines for bullying in schools",
        "additional_details": "Put into place new laws and fines that if a child should bully another either physically or emotionally that a stepped level of punishment should be as follows:\r\n\r\n1st instance: a warning letter home and detention for the child \r\n\r\n2nd instance: A fine of \u00a330 (a 50% percentage paid towards victim) and warning that should it happen again a greater fine would be imposed. Plus suspension for 1 week of student. \r\n\r\n3rd instance: fine to be imposed based on level of severity\r\n",
        "background": "Due to being a parent of a bullied child, seeing that schools are plagued by this problem yet seem to find it difficult to tackle I propose this to the government:",
